text_en:
That form of his…
that evil heart…
If we must name him… Jagan.{END}

Revival…
What he needs for that is…
a physical body!?{END}

Yes… Did any of your eras
have a capsule containing
an eerie organism?{END}

…I thought so.
He is using this timeline
to make it grow.{END}

There is only one way
to keep him from gaining
a physical form.{END}
